CASE    WHEN SUBSTR(REGEXP_REPLACE(user_phone_number,'[^0-9]',''),1,3) = '62-' THEN REGEXP_REPLACE(user_phone_number,'[^0-9]','')
                            WHEN SUBSTR(REGEXP_REPLACE(user_phone_number,'[^0-9]',''),1,2) = '62' THEN CONCAT(SUBSTR(REGEXP_REPLACE(user_phone_number,'[^0-9]',''),1,2),'-',SUBSTR(REGEXP_REPLACE(user_phone_number,'[^0-9]',''),3))
                            WHEN SUBSTR(REGEXP_REPLACE(user_phone_number,'[^0-9]',''),1,2) = '08' THEN CONCAT('62-',SUBSTR(REGEXP_REPLACE(user_phone_number,'[^0-9]',''),2))
                            ELSE CONCAT('62-',REGEXP_REPLACE(user_phone_number,'[^0-9]',''))
                    END

CASE WHEN user_phone_number RLIKE '^62' THEN CONCAT('62-',SUBSTR(user_phone_number,3)) WHEN user_phone_number RLIKE '^08' THEN CONCAT('62-',SUBSTR(user_phone_number,2)) WHEN user_phone_number RLIKE '^8' THEN CONCAT('62-',user_phone_number) ELSE CONCAT('62-',user_phone_number) END

CASE WHEN contact_phone_number RLIKE '^62' THEN CONCAT('62-',SUBSTR(contact_phone_number,3)) WHEN contact_phone_number RLIKE '^08' THEN CONCAT('62-',SUBSTR(contact_phone_number,2)) WHEN contact_phone_number RLIKE '^8' THEN CONCAT('62-',contact_phone_number) ELSE CONCAT('62-',contact_phone_number) END
